OL,3,CPharmacy treatments saving more than a
OL,4,Cthousand GP appointments a month
OL,6,FMore than a thousand GP appointments a
OL,7,Fmonth have been freed up in Cornwall
OL,8,Fin a pilot where people can get
OL,9,Ftreatment for certain conditions from
OL,10,Fa pharmacist instead.
OL,12,FThe Pharmacy First scheme has been so
OL,13,Fsuccessful it's now being rolled out
OL,14,Facross the country.
OL,16,FFrom sore throats to shingles,
OL,17,Fpharmacists can diagnose and treat a
OL,18,Frange of common conditions on the spot.
