OL,3,CPharmacy treatments saving more than a
OL,4,Cthousand GP appointments a month
OL,6,FPharmacist Jakob Solarz from Penryn
OL,7,Fsaid: "We can avoid referring people
OL,8,Fwho suffer from quite common and
OL,9,Funcomplicated conditions back to their
OL,10,FGP.
OL,12,F"So we can see them quicker, give them
OL,13,Fthe medication that they need without
OL,14,Fhaving to book an appointment with
OL,15,Ftheir GP."
OL,17,FThe pilot scheme has been running for
OL,18,Ftwo years in Cornwall, and over the
OL,19,Flast year, it's saved 12,000 GP
OL,20,Fappointments.
