OL,3,CPharmacy treatments saving more than a
OL,4,Cthousand GP appointments a month
OL,6,FDr Chris Reid, Chief Medical Officer,
OL,7,FNHS Cornwall and Isles of Scilly
OL,8,FIntegrated Care Board said: "I've been
OL,9,Fa GP for more than 20 years. I know
OL,10,Fhow busy we are and I know how
OL,11,Fimportant community pharmacies are.
OL,13,F"They play a part in what I would call
OL,14,Fa 'team of teams' approach to making
OL,15,Fsure we've got a really good offering
OL,16,Fto access full access for patients
OL,17,Fwhen they need it so they can get the
OL,18,Fright care in the right place at the
OL,19,Fright time and take the pressure off
OL,20,Fthe emergency departments as well."
