OL,3,CPharmacy treatments saving more than a
OL,4,Cthousand GP appointments a month
OL,6,FDrew Creek, chief operating officer,
OL,7,Fof community pharmacy in Cornwall
OL,8,Fsaid: "People will find it easy to
OL,9,Faccess their pharmacy. They don't need
OL,10,Fan appointment.
OL,12,F"They can just walk in. Yes, there
OL,13,Fmight be a short wait as our pharmacy
OL,14,Fteams are very busy, but pharmacies
OL,15,Fhave some capacity within their day to
OL,16,Fbe able to deliver this new service
OL,17,Fand see patients in the consultation
OL,18,Froom."
